      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Emran Mian is the interim Director General for Strategy and International. He was the Acting Director General for Higher Education and Further Education at the Department for Education (<abbr title="Department for Education">DfE</abbr>) between October 2018 and January 2019.</p>

<p>Since returning to the Civil Service in February 2017, Emran has been Director of Strategy and Social Mobility. Previously he ran the Social Market Foundation, a cross-party think tank.</p>

<p>Earlier in his career he held senior positions in both the Cabinet Office and Business Department</p>

</div>
      </section>

